item.title: CVE-2022-2912|2024-08-03T00:52:59.857Z -- unknown -- craw%20data
item.description: The Craw Data WordPress plugin through 1.0.0 does not implement nonce checks, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change the url value performing unwanted crawls on third-party sites (SSRF).
